
Overview of noun martyr

The noun martyr has 2 senses (first 1 from tagged texts)
                                         
1. (8) martyr, sufferer -- (one who suffers for the sake of principle)
2. martyr -- (one who voluntarily suffers death as the penalty for refusing to renounce their religion)

